<div class="container mt-5 about-section">
    <h2 class="text-center">About Me</h2>
    <p>Hi, I'm Sawsan, a passionate web developer with a solid foundation in .NET technologies. I specialize in backend development using C#, ASP.NET Core, and SQL Server, and I have extensive experience building full-stack web applications with modern frameworks like Blazor. I'm committed to continuous learning and improving my skills to stay up-to-date with the latest trends in the industry.</p>

    <h3>My Journey</h3>
    <p>I began my programming journey with a strong focus on problem-solving, which naturally led me to explore various programming languages and frameworks. Over time, I've refined my skills in web development, and I am currently deeply immersed in .NET and cloud technologies, particularly Microsoft Azure.</p>

    <h3>Skills & Technologies</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>C#</li>
        <li>ASP.NET Core</li>
        <li>SQL Server</li>
        <li>Blazor</li>
        <li>HTML, CSS</li>
        <li>Git and GitHub</li>
        <p>To dive deeper into the technologies I specialize in, check out my <a href="/Skills">Skills</a> page.</p>
    </ul>

    <h3>My Projects</h3>
    <p>I have contributed to several web development projects, ranging from small applications to large-scale enterprise systems. For a detailed overview of my work, please visit my <a href="/Project">Projects</a> page.</p>

    <h3>Education</h3>
    <p>I am currently pursuing a degree in Computer Science and Information at Tanta University, where I continue to explore cutting-edge technologies and trends in the field of software development.</p>

    <h3>Contact Me</h3>
    <p>If you'd like to connect or collaborate, please feel free to reach out to me via my <a href="/Home/Contact">Contact</a> page.</p>

